  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A traditional continental breakfast spread is served each morning with cakes, pastries, fresh fruits and yogurts as well as cold cuts and cheeses. Hot options are also provided. </p>
<p>In the evenings, the garden view restaurant offers up traditional Italian dishes such as homemade gnocchi, pasta and freshly cooked pizzas along with a salad bar and dessert choice. If you opt for half board you'll have a three course meal in the restaurant, with choices. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
