  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Bella <a data-udi="umb://document/0f9f33f516a448a2ab8bda68f2fba594" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0f9f33f516a448a2ab8bda68f2fba594}" title="Peschiera">Peschiera</a> is a lovely three-star hotel with contemporary rooms and nice public areas. Although small, you’ll find everything you need here. A pool is at the back of the hotel in the gardens and it’s a lovely place to relax. A restaurant serves up traditional Italian food for dinner and a continental breakfast to get you going in the mornings. You’ll also be able to use the facilities at Bella Italia Villaggio (about ten minutes away) including the pool and evening entertainment. They have a spa too, which you can book and pay for locally.</p>
<p>The location of the hotel is really convenient. The centre is less than five minutes away so you can explore the town and walk along the lakefront. The ferry port connects you to resorts along the lake like <a data-udi="umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1}" title="Bardolino">Bardolino</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/0f9f33f516a448a2ab8bda68f2fba594" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0f9f33f516a448a2ab8bda68f2fba594}" title="Peschiera">Sirmione</a>. There’s a train station too with regular trains to <a data-udi="umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/201893063f65496384a9bd17846543a7}" title="Venice">Venice</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/41229767036d47f28a27ac846e23458b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/41229767036d47f28a27ac846e23458b}" title="Verona">Verona</a>.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 45 mins by coach from Verona airport.</p>]]></description>
