  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This is a small but perfectly formed hotel. It's got comtemporary rooms, a nice restaurant and a colourful garden with a pool. It's close to the centre of Peschiera too and the perfect base for if you want to explore - either by boat or train.</p>
<p> </p>]]></listingDescription>
