  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double Rooms</strong> have a balcony and lake views. They can sleep up to four people. The third and fourth bed are available on request and the extra beds are a single bed or bunk beds. These rooms have double beds. Facilities include air conditioning, TV, safe, hairdryer and walk-in shower. If you'd like a room with two separate single beds, they are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Double Rooms for Sole Use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
